lead_paragraph: Andrew Andrews matched his career-high with 35 points, including five straight points midway through the second overtime, and Washington held on to beat No. 25 UCLA 96-93 in double overtime on Friday night in a game that featured 64 fouls.

headline.print_headline: Andrews Scores 35, Washington Beats No. 25 UCLA 96-93 in 2OT
